/build/
release/
# Wails desktop build dir: ignore generated output, but keep the Linux packaging
# assets (hicolor icon tree + .desktop) which are committed source. The first
# negation overrides a global "build/" ignore so the linux/ subtree is reachable.
!cmd/desktop/build/
cmd/desktop/build/*
!cmd/desktop/build/linux/
cmd/desktop/frontend/dist/
frontend/dist/
frontend/node_modules/
*.app
.DS_Store
Makefile
